{"type": "article", "id": 25094, "title": "「这世界」健身房里的难言之隐，全都藏在这 31 张名画里", "description": "欢迎对号入座！", "date": "2016-04-07T13:44:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1543, "name": "这世界"}, {"id": 4759, "name": "健身"}, {"id": 25937, "name": "名画"}], "category": 5, "column": 13, "author": 4695, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 396, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134508GXN9UP3x1TECpoqt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>Buzzfeed 做了个专题，借用 31 张著名油画描述了大家在健身房里的状态。特别厉害，大家可以一起来看一看。<br></p>\n<p>1.  当你走进一家健身房，销售试图让你买两年会员。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134452OfmPIt4wWK2ylNnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>2.  当你打算喝 pre-workout 补充剂前会小心翼翼地确认它是不是合法的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134453mOEDvHa69PSnoL0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>3.  当你在练器械，有人跑来让你走开给他们练。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134453gl5MYx72OqPsKIE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72595281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>4.  当健身房里都是火辣的身体，你眼睛都不知道往哪儿看了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134454XbTCM8hpI0jWkiEe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>5.  当你进了更衣室，大家都在忙着照镜子和自拍。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134455dLc4l9hzYKtnvUjg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>6.  ……除了有个人光着身子在到处转悠。不过没人关心。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344555ksClPIUaemG2oKV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7712\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>7.  当你和你的朋友分享健身计划表的样子。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344566aiHLJcR0mVoAPGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>8.  当你和一个陌生人配成一组训练。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134456UAuYZr2bGhjsJeOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>9.  当你问一个身材超级好的人能不能用用他的哑铃。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134457yb25uXDtENHLOgwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16960352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>10.  当更衣室终于谈起了健康饮食的话题，你开始意识到健康食品并不都像它们吹嘘的那样。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344578r7U5fdsvLghD01q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>11.  ……但起码你可以想想自己最终有一个好身材的样子。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134458TlDeS0tv5RfOzBKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3728\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>12.  当你看到那个家伙的身体特别大块儿，以至于头看起来很小。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134458eUYh26FW4P7zMO80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.942\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>13.  当有人问你是不是要报个班和大家一起上课。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134459kz3eTwWxVjUFOcDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>14.  当你最终选了尊巴课并且爱死它了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134500VMgpkLG64n57Te8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>15.  当你花大价钱买了运动服、锻炼鞋、 iPhone 臂戴、护腕和一切装备，在更衣室把它们换上后。“该死，我真好看。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134500MejFk51Tnig4aLDz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.52666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>16.  当你跑步机设置得太快害自己摔倒，然后工作人员来救你。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134501fC9Evl6cAsamJGbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>17、当你的教练拿棍子戳你让你再来一组的时候。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134501UbKvm6X91JNrHCYT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>18.  当音乐节奏突然停了，你的杠铃操突然变得手忙脚乱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345022El5Vt1JasbSrNmp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24016563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>19.  当你想中途退出锻炼，因为美的标准太不可理喻了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134502mzgrUICix9D3Ay7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>20.  当那种无差别搭讪狂在健身房里靠近你并开始勾搭你。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134503NovzCmO5HsrwDkTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97087379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>21.  当你庆祝完成了一套特别难的臀部训练。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134503mQbfpoeCy5as3RTh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>22.  当你和你的朋友讨论镜中可爱的人儿。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134504tRUQCyKjks8Ii0oB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62383178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>23.  当你第一次学普拉提，做出来动作很难看。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134504deGPwuYFE0zVZC4c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.264\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>24.  当你看到有人用完器械没擦干净。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134505P7804RxTBlVWn6HD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>25.  当你意识到你两个月的会员费花了多少钱，而自己一次也没去。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345057O8VIqYB5WZyLtbP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01018676\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>26.  当你的教练给你放松肌肉而你毫无感觉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345051erdIUin3C96bcQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6784\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>27.  当 1 月 22 日健身房里挤满了人，所有人都被它的新年新规弄疯了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134506uj5t9gb48CSmnEB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>28.  ……然后到了 8 月，当时的人群早就不在了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134506te34XLoqDu2AFghH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>29.  当你离开健身房，并捧着 post-workout 餐大快朵颐。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134507Ei9N8Hy0MQdGOoju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>30.  ……但是之后又开始担心会发胖。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134507mcRQVTMo3ZIfnSNK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.832\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>31.  最后，当你锻炼得半死不活回到家，却发觉室友买了一堆烤串。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134508gjf7hCJiVUAp8SbB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a target=\"_blank\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjbnf_78PvLAhUIzmMKHb9xCy4QjB0IBg&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2F101193079%40N05%2F17183925674&amp;psig=AFQjCNFxAgvuQYVgk-Qz_7plx1uzBbLixQ&amp;ust=1460083390738710\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjbnf_78PvLAhUIzmMKHb9xCy4QjB0IBg\" data-href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/101193079@N05/17183925674\">www.flickr.com</a><br></p>\n\n"}